             was indicted for <rs id="t17900224-9-off58" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17900224-9-off58" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17900224-9-off58" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17900224-9-cd59" type="crimeDate">19th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900224-9-off58 t17900224-9-cd59"></join>, in the parish of St. Ann, Westminster, three woollen blankets, value 10 s. one woollen rug, value 10 s. two pieces of cotton, value 5 s. and a man's cloth coat, value 5 s.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17900224-9-victim145" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Clarke
                  <interp inst="t17900224-9-victim145" type="surname" value="Clarke"></interp>
