                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900224-9-defend143 t17900224-9-punish64"></join>
               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. Baron THOMPSON.</p>
